  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical diagnosis of bleeding peptic ulcer and active bleeding after ESD/EMR

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Coagulation disorder (PLT &lt; 50*10^9/L, INR &gt; 2)

          -  Connot stop taking the antiplatelet drug, NSAID, Anticoagulant drug, and Aspirin
             during endoscopic treatment and after 72h endoscopy
      </textblock>
